1. *Ovisiš* o meni previše. (You rely on me too much.)
2. *Ovisno* o vremenskim uslovima, idemo u park ili na plažu. (Depending on the weather conditions, we'll go to the park or the beach.)
3. Ne mogu ti tačno reći, to *ovisi* od mnogih faktora. (I can't tell you exactly, it depends on many factors.)
4. *Ovisiš* o drogama da bi se osećao dobro. (You depend on drugs to feel good.)
5. *Ovisnost* o kocki može dovesti do velikih problema. (Gambling addiction can lead to big problems.)
6. *Ovisnost* o tehnologiji postaje sve veći problem. (Technology addiction is becoming a bigger problem.)
7. *Ovisni* smo o našim mobilnim telefonima. (We are addicted to our mobile phones.)
8. *Ne ovisi* sve o novcu u životu. (Not everything in life depends on money.)